{
  "texts": [
    "The mean N170 amplitudes for all stimulus types are extracted and tested against each other in a one-way repeated measurement ANOVA (rmANOVA) with the factor stimulus type (Face vs. Blurred vs.",
    "Scrambled).",
    "Specifically, the amplitudes for the N170 are extracted for the literature-based electrodes (i.a., P8/P7, PO8/PO7, P10/P9) and a manually defined time-window (165 -205 ms).",
    "The classifier performed on average with 64% accuracy on the test set.",
    "The standard deviation was 0.025."
  ]
}